---
title: Shawarma Roasted Aubergine with Chickpeas, Mushrooms and Nutty Tomato Salsa
description: Black peppercorns, cinnamon, cardamom, cumin and coriander are just a few of the ingredients that go into our delicious shawarma spice mix. With that many strings to its bow, it’s hard to believe that this spicy blend doesn’t completely steal the show. But when the competition is as good as a spicy mushroom and chickpea stew, and a fresh walnut and tomato salsa, it’s hard to put a finger on the winner. We’ll let you decide!
